Region Wise Yearly Wage

2. Region wise Yearly Wage:

Drag and drop region and year in column shelves and Hourly wage in row shelves



Go to Mark shelves and drop down arrow button and select Bar chart.

One more time drag and drop Hourly wage in row shelves.


Click on dual axis chart in second hourly wage rate.


Drag and drop Year in filters and choose Years then click Next.


choose only 4 years and click ok .


Right click Hourly wages then click Mark Type and Circle.


Drag and drop Measure Names in color card .


Click on SUM(Hourlywages)then click Color and Edit Colors choose color then click OK.


Right click on Hourly wage select Quick Table Calculation then select percentile option.


Drag and drop Measure Names in color card and Click T 


Click on SUM (Hourly wages) then click Size.
